# Restart-to-apply-language confirmation (added 2026-06-06).

msgid "Restart to change the language?"
msgstr "重启以更改语言？"

msgid "The new language is loaded only after a restart. Restart now, or do it yourself later."
msgstr "新语言仅在重启后加载。立即重启，或稍后自行重启。"

msgid "Later"
msgstr "稍后"

msgid "Restart now"
msgstr "立即重启"

# Mini-player: tap the song display to open the track detail view (added 2026-06-07).

msgid "Show details of the current track"
msgstr "显示当前曲目的详细信息"

# Sort popover: discreet toggle to sort without section headings (added 2026-06-07).

msgid "Without grouping"
msgstr "不分组"

# Settings → Library: confirm before removing an extra source (added 2026-06-07).

msgid "Remove this source?"
msgstr "移除此来源？"

# Menu section descriptions + YouTube settings text (added 2026-06-07).

msgid "YouTube uses the bundled yt-dlp tool. Since YouTube frequently breaks older versions, you can update it to a newer one here. Turn the YouTube section itself on under Menu. May be restricted in some countries."
msgstr "YouTube 使用随应用附带的 yt-dlp 工具。由于 YouTube 经常使旧版本失效，你可以在此将其更新为较新版本。在“菜单”中开启 YouTube 板块本身。某些国家或地区可能受限。"

msgid "Quick access to the tracks, albums and artists you starred."
msgstr "快速访问你加星标的曲目、专辑和艺术家。"

msgid "Browse your music folder — and any extra sources — as a file tree."
msgstr "以文件树方式浏览你的音乐文件夹以及任何额外来源。"

msgid "Every artist in your library, each opening to their albums and tracks."
msgstr "媒体库中的每位艺术家，点开即见其专辑和曲目。"

msgid "Every album in your library, sortable and grouped by initial or year."
msgstr "媒体库中的每张专辑，可排序并按首字母或年份分组。"

msgid "Live and concert recordings you marked, kept apart from your albums."
msgstr "你标记的演唱会和现场录音，与普通专辑分开。"

msgid "Subscribe to podcast feeds and play or download their episodes."
msgstr "订阅播客源，播放或下载其剧集。"

msgid "Internet radio stations, with an optional buffer to record what just played."
msgstr "网络电台，可选缓冲以录制刚刚播放的内容。"

msgid "Search and play YouTube, follow channels and keep videos offline. Needs the yt-dlp tool."
msgstr "搜索并播放 YouTube、关注频道并离线保存视频。需要 yt-dlp 工具。"

msgid "Albums, folders or tracks you marked as audiobooks, resuming where you left off."
msgstr "你标记为有声书的专辑、文件夹或曲目，可从上次位置继续。"

msgid "Your own playlists, arranged in any order you like."
msgstr "你自己的播放列表，可按任意顺序排列。"

msgid "Quick voice notes recorded with the microphone."
msgstr "用麦克风录制的快速语音备忘。"

msgid "Listening statistics and your most-played artists and tracks."
msgstr "收听统计以及你最常播放的艺术家和曲目。"
